@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.80) - tmp)
    v1 = wp.cos(v1)
    v1 = (v2 / (v2 + v1))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.sin(v1))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp((tmp + 0.88 / v2 + 0.31)))
    tmp = 0.31
    tmp = 0.57
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.79 - v0 + 0.38) + v0) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.57 - v1 + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
